# 安得家政小程序 API 接口文档

> 域名：crm.andejiazheng.com/api
> 认证方式：除标注【公开】外，均需 Bearer Token（CRM员工账号）
> 与「安得褓贝」小程序的区分：本文档为家政业务侧（员工/管理端）使用的接口

---

## 一、认证服务（auth）

| # | 方法 | URL | 认证 | 说明 |
|---|------|-----|------|------|
| 1 | POST | /auth/miniprogram-login | 公开 | CRM员工小程序登录（微信code换token） |
| 2 | GET  | /auth/me | Token | 获取当前登录员工信息 |

---

## 二、线索 / 客户管理（customers）⭐

| # | 方法 | URL | 认证 | 说明 |
|---|------|-----|------|------|
| 3 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/statistics | Token | 获取客户统计信息（基于角色权限） |
| 4 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/today-todo-stats | Token | 获取今日待办统计 |
| 5 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/performance-progress | Token | 获取业绩进度 |
| 6 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/contract-stats | Token | 获取合同统计 |
| 7 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/list | Token | 获取客户列表（权限控制+数据脱敏） |
| 8 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/employees/list | Token | 获取员工列表（用于分配客户） |
| 9 | POST | /customers/miniprogram/create | Token | 创建客户线索（支持幂等性） |
| 10 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/:id | Token | 获取客户详情（权限控制） |
| 11 | PATCH | /customers/miniprogram/:id | Token | 更新客户信息 |
| 12 | PATCH | /customers/miniprogram/:id/assign | Token | 分配客户（仅管理员/经理） |
| 13 | POST | /customers/miniprogram/:id/follow-ups | Token | 创建客户跟进记录 |
| 14 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/:id/follow-ups | Token | 获取客户跟进记录列表 |
| 15 | GET | /customers/miniprogram/:id/assignment-logs | Token | 获取客户分配历史 |
| 16 | POST | /customers/miniprogram/:id/release-to-pool | Token | 释放客户到公海 |

---

## 三、合同管理（contracts/miniprogram）

| # | 方法 | URL | 认证 | 说明 |
|---|------|-----|------|------|
| 17 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/list | Token | 获取合同列表 |
| 18 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/statistics | Token | 获取合同统计信息 |
| 19 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/check-customer/:customerPhone | Token | 检查客户现有合同 |
| 20 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/history/:customerPhone | Token | 获取客户合同历史 |
| 21 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/search-worker | Token | 根据服务人员信息搜索合同 |
| 22 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/by-customer/:customerId | Token | 根据客户ID获取合同列表 |
| 23 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/by-worker-id/:workerId | Token | 根据服务人员ID获取合同列表 |
| 24 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/by-number/:contractNumber | Token | 根据合同编号获取合同 |
| 25 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/detail/:id | Token | 获取合同详情 |
| 26 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/esign-info/:id | Token | 获取合同爱签信息 |
| 27 | GET | /contracts/miniprogram/signers-status/:id | Token | 获取签署方详细状态 |
| 28 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/validate | Token | 验证合同数据 |
| 29 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/create | Token | 创建合同 |
| 30 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/initiate-signing/:id | Token | 发起电子签署 |
| 31 | PUT | /contracts/miniprogram/update/:id | Token | 更新合同 |
| 32 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/change-worker/:originalContractId | Token | 创建换人合同 |
| 33 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/resend-sign-urls/:id | Token | 重新获取签署链接 |
| 34 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/download-contract/:id | Token | 下载已签署合同 |
| 35 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/withdraw/:id | Token | 撤销合同 |
| 36 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/invalidate/:id | Token | 作废合同 |
| 37 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/cancel/:id | Token | 智能撤销/作废合同 |
| 38 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/sync-insurance/:id | Token | 手动触发保险同步 |
| 39 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/sync-esign-status/:id | Token | 同步爱签合同状态 |
| 40 | POST | /contracts/miniprogram/sync-all-esign-status | Token | 批量同步所有合同爱签状态 |

